        },
        "actions": {
          "value": null
        },
        "category": "defensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Incorporeal; resistance all 8 (except force/vitality); rejuvenates 2d6 rounds after destruction and stays passive unless attacked again. He is bound by guilt while Ileosa lives; her defeat — and his bones honored in the crypts (A3) — lets him rest.</p>"
